  "title": "Embedded Systems Engineer (Aerospace)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>In charge of designing the PCB layout of electronic circuit boards and generate Gerber files for PCB fabrication.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in research and define efficient and reliable architecture to fulfil electronic circuit board requirements for the company drone systems.</li>\n  <li>In charge of firmware programming in embedded C/C++ language.</li>\n  <li>In charge of testing PCB assemblies thoroughly and ensure they operate as expected.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in sourcing suitable electronic components to implement the design architecture.</li>\n  <li>In charge of studying datasheets of the electronic components and design the schematic of electronic circuit boards that can fulfil the requirements.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in generateing documents and drawings of design and test.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Degree in Mechanical/ Electrical/ Aerospace/ Mechatronics Engineering or relevant</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of working experience in electronic hardware and firmware design</li>\n  <li>Experience in analog and digital circuit design with experience in designing electronic circuits with microcontrollers, digital signal processors (DSP), field programmable gate arrays (FPGAs), etc</li>\n  <li>Proficient in schematic and PCB design tools such as Altium Designer, OrCAD Capture and PCB Designer, Autodesk EAGLE, etc and using instruments such as multimeters, oscilloscopes, logic analysers, etc. to troubleshoot issues on electronic circuit boards.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in C/C++ programming language.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge in various communication buses and protocols such as UART, I2C, SPI, CAN, Ethernet, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br>\n<strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
